<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5356452>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Marsupials from Laguna Fría (LF) and La Barda (LB). A, Peradectidae gen. et sp. nov., LIEB- PV 1031 (LF); B, Caroloameghiniidae gen. et sp. nov., LIEB-PV 1098 (LF); C, Peradectoidea gen. et sp. nov., LIEB-PV 1097, left M3 (LB); D, Protodidelphis sp. nov., LIEB-PV 1091, left M?3 (LB); E, Pauladelphys sp. nov., LIEB-PV 1123, m2 in a fragment of right dentary (LF); F, cf. Itaboraidelphys sp., LIEB-PV 1064, an isolated right m2 or m3 (LF); G, Paucituberculata gen. et sp. nov. 1, LIEB-PV 1135, a left maxillary fragment with M2–3 and part of M4 (LF); H, Sparassodonta, Hathliacynidae, gen. et sp. nov. LIEB-PV 1036, M?3 in a maxillary fragment (LF); I, Eomicrobiotherium sp., LIEB-PV 1040, a right m?3 (LF); J, Palangania sp., LIEB-PV 1106, left M?3 (LB); K, Gashternia ctalehor, LIEB-PV 1132, a right M4 (LB)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5356452/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

